Organics thought this over.  She had come so close, what was the harm in seeing this Malice character.  She decended, and hitched her sheild and sword on her back.  See walked over to the Maximal.  She was tall, almost as tall as Malice.
"Lead on then."

airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
OOC: HEHEHEHEHEHEH Windlord is HE!!!!!!

Windlord looked that the Lady was loosing her patient and he decided 
to be diplomatic "Excuse me, Madam, But the only bounty hunter that 
we have is Malice... Would you will follow me in order to see if 
he 's the bot that you're looking for?"




"In the name of God, I banish these souls of the evil undead into damnation.  May God have mercy, for I have none.  In Jesus' Holy Name, Amen." -Rawl, Hellsing-RPG
